## World Bible Contents

`docs/world-bible.md` is the canonical source for:

| Topic | Content |
|-------|---------|
| Cosmology | The origin of the world, the Void, the Heavenly Stairway |
| 10 Realms | Full definitions with mechanics |
| 8 Regions | Climate, specialty, sect bonus, hazard |
| 50 Sects | Names, alignment, rank, benefits, HQ |
| 5 Resources | Currencies with acquisition and sink |
| NPC Pantheon | Celestial bureaucracy, regional NPCs |
| Factions | Chính Đạo, Tà Đạo, Trung Lập |
| Tribulations | Types and severity |
| World Timeline | Major eras and events |

