## Sect Design Standards

Every sect in the World Bible and Knowledge Base MUST have:

| Field | Example |
|-------|---------|
| **ID** | `THANH_VAN_TONG` |
| **Name** | Thanh Vân Tông |
| **Region** | Đại Việt |
| **Alignment** | Chính Đạo |
| **Rank** | ★★★ |
| **Headquarters** | Thanh Vân Sơn |
| **Signature Art** | Thanh Vân Kiếm Quyết |
| **Specialty** | Thủy công, luyện đan |
| **Benefits** | +10% cultivation, +20% healing |
| **Internal Conflict** | Old guard vs reformist |
| **Enemy** | Vạn Độc Giáo |
| **Ally** | Chính Dương Tông |

### Sect Personality

Each sect should feel distinct:

- **Thanh Vân Tông**: Elegant, scholarly, slightly aloof. Their members speak carefully and value precision.
- **Võ Đang Phái**: Disciplined, martial, honor-bound. Direct speech, respect hierarchy.
- **Vạn Độc Giáo**: Calculating, ruthless, pragmatic. Will negotiate before betraying.
- **U Minh Môn**: Ominous, cryptic, patient. Short sentences, lots of silence.

---

## NPC Design Standards

Every major NPC in the knowledge base MUST have:

| Field | Content |
|-------|---------|
| **Name** | Unique identifier |
| **Title** | Formal title (e.g., "Lương Y") |
| **Affiliation** | Sect or independent |
| **Location** | Where they can be found |
| **Role** | Quest giver, shop keeper, lore source |
| **Personality** | 2-3 sentences |
| **Voice** | How they speak (see dialogue guide) |
| **Quirk** | One memorable detail |
| **Knowledge** | What they know about the world |

